<td><FONT SIZE="1" FACE="Verdana, Arial" COLOR="#D0BC90">Originally posted by Highlander on 10-26-2002 06:52 PM<BR></FONT>
<TEXTAREA NAME="EditedMessage" ROWS=20 COLS=75 WRAP="VIRTUAL">Well after a lot of late nights, the wife complaining about me wasting away in from of my PC and large amounts of both coffee & ciggaretes, i have finally beat this game!!!!

I must say i like RPG's and its good to see a game that is like a good book and can't be put down. Lots of fun, lots of enemies & lots of choice. Only 1 thing i thought odd, (maybe im just a picky sod) When equiping various items it would be nice to see the character holding or wearing that item, a few item in inventory look different but when equipped they look the same, But Excellent game.

Ok for anyone who likes stats, or for anyone yet to play,(heres what to expect). Here are my end of game stats.

Level - 48 Warrior
Exp - 38714994
Vitality - 1210 / 1210
Magic 1017 / 1017
Strength - 145
Agility - 115
Intelligence - 79
Constitution - 95

Offence - 96
Defence - 91
Damage - 93 - 128
Armour - 282

Lightning resistance - 55
Fire resistance - 90
Poison resistance - 100
Spirit resistance - 120

Reputation - 36

Weight - 2278 / 4500
Gold - 67121

And after lots of adding i killed a total of "6410" monsters. Minus a few bosses.

Damn i love this game!!

------------------
There can only be ONE - (and thats me)</TEXTAREA>
